      public <MSG extends BASE> PayloadChannel.Builder.Flow<BUF,BASE> add(CustomPacketPayload.Type<MSG> type, StreamCodec<BUF,MSG> codec, BiConsumer<MSG,CustomPayloadEvent.Context> consumer)
      从接口复制的说明: PayloadFlow
      Adds a packet to this channel that has it's protocol validated whenever sent or received.

      The handler is called on the network thread, and so should not interact with most game state by default. CustomPayloadEvent.Context.enqueueWork(Runnable) can be used to handle the message on the main server or client thread.
